{"tid":1252391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那蝗係香港絕對敵畜，任何偽人返支那賣屎忽即為香港公敵","createTime":"2019-06-23T03:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T11:42:03.000Z","uid":182935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"92e6e8adaf8418c31032ef974e2ebf72c5133b61","tid":1252391,"uid":182935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係時候再發起呢個運動</span></strong><br />\n我們的堅持，就是只接受&ldquo;忠港藝人&rdquo;&nbsp;<br />\n重申一次&ldquo;忠港藝人&rdquo;定義&nbsp;<br />\n1.正宗香港本土出生&nbsp;<br />\n2.只拍本土電影電視&nbsp;<br />\n3.只唱香港話歌曲&nbsp;<br />\n4.力撐香港有真民主,真普選,如果支持香港有自冶甚至獨立則更佳&nbsp;<br />\n5.永遠抵制一切支那宣傳活動,堅決不上支那進行一切公開活動(包括拍片開show出席活動甚至唱蝗語歌，一句都唔得)&nbsp;<br />\n6.抵制一切支那宣傳產品(包括微博QQ微信等...)&nbsp;<br />\n以上缺一不可,只要任何一項不符合,即可視為港奸賣港賊，我們必定予以永久杯葛&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n香港藝人,必須固守香港，以香港為家，￼&nbsp;拒絕一切支那利誘￼&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n另:以上第4至6條款適用範圍不限於本地藝人，也適用於海外藝人以至ACG作品<br />\n<br />\n請支持&ldquo;全面抵制北上偽人&rdquo;專頁&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=1525653001015579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fid%3D1525653001015579&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=400b8266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=1525653001015579</a>"},{"pid":"73fd97ec537fc8120b5e834d213970adf5296e07","tid":1252391,"uid":182935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"h